gnification en droit) à appréhender cette question. Ils analysent ce point précis où une « forme de vie » manifeste davantage de vie que le discours est lui-même capable de supporter.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aEffectiveness and validity of law. 0aKnowledge, Theory of. 0aLawxPhilosophy. 0aSciencexPhilosophy. 7aLAW / Arbitration, Negotiation, Mediation.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311127221408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021z978311127464540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763747231?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763747231423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763747231/original  a978-3-11-127221-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-127464-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles